Bruce,

With the thousands of Elvis impersonators out there, many of them who 
have crossed over, do you think maybe one of them came through for 
you?
I knew a person who was hand picked by Elvis to work for him at 
Graceland in the early days at Graceland.  Maybe the next time &quot;he&quot; 
comes through you can inquire as to the name of this person I know, 
that he knows.
This person was &quot;very special&quot; to him and she was hand picked by 
Elvis based on her looks (she told me that), even though the duties 
she provided at Graceland were none such that good looks were 
required.

I&#39;m hoping if it is Elvis, he will know who you are inquiring about. 
Only he would know this, not an Elvis impersonator.

Tell him her father&#39;s last name begins with the letter &quot;R&quot; and he 
traveled with &quot;MP&quot;.  He only needs to give you her first name.

With this information I have provided, there is no doubt that &quot;he&quot; 
will know who you are asking about.

- Mike

